The new play-by-play announcer for Yankee games on the Madison Square Garden network is DeWayne Staats, who has been announcing Cubs games for five seasons. . . . Mark Breland, the World Boxing Association welterweight champion, will defend his title for the third time, against Fujio Ozaki of Japan in Tokyo on Dec. 10. . . . Art Boileau of Canada and Zoya Ivanova of the Soviet Union, winners of the 1989 Los Angeles Marathon, have entered next Sunday's New York City Marathon.
